Hm. Are you sure this works? I thought this would give you a different reference, when you need the same for both add/remove... I've always done this like:

```
this.unwatchPrefs = this.unwatchPrefs.bind(this);
addListener(this.unwatchPrefs);
/* later... */
removeListener(this.unwatchPrefs);
```
